name: Childhood treasure#2
description: When I was a kid, there were chewing gums with pictures of football players, me and kids my age were betting and playing with these pictures, and whoever won was like a kingdom with a great treasure, and our dream was to have as many of these pictures as possible. , My family always told me these are worthless, but for me these were treasures. I kept this treasure of my childhood for 25 years and today I decided to make it NFT. Maybe someone's childhood memory came alive, maybe someone lost his childhood treasure. I present these photos in a single edition.
